name: The Shield Is Down!
Lore: 'Lando''s confidence in the Rebel strike team on the forest moon was rewarded, and proved to be a decisive factor at the Battle of Endor.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. If Rebel Strike Team on table, your Force generation is +1 at Endor sites and you may deploy Back Door from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. When Bunker ''blown away,'' retrieve 8 Force and opponent must place their hand in Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
